#. module: sale_project_stock
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/sale_project_stock/models/stock_picking.py:0
msgid ""
"The Sales Order %(order)s linked to the Project %(project)s is cancelled. "
"You cannot validate a stock picking on a cancelled Sales Order."
msgstr ""
"ໃບສັ່ງຂາຍ %(order)s ທີ່ເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ກັບ ໂຄງການ %(project)s ຖືກຍົກເລີກແລ້ວ. ທ່ານບໍ່ສາມາດຢືນຢັນການເບີກ"
"ສາງໃນໃບສັ່ງຂາຍທີ່ຖືກຍົກເລີກໄດ້."

#. module: sale_project_stock
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/sale_project_stock/models/stock_picking.py:0
msgid ""
"The Sales Order %(order)s linked to the Project %(project)s is currently "
"locked. You cannot validate a stock picking on a locked Sales Order. Please "
"create a new SO linked to this Project."
msgstr ""
"ໃບສັ່ງຂາຍ %(order)s ທີ່ເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ກັບ ໂຄງການ %(project)s ຖືກລັອກໄວ້ໃນຂະນະນີ້. ທ່ານບໍ່ສາມາດຢືນຢັນກາ"
"ນເບີກສາງໃນໃບສັ່ງຂາຍທີ່ຖືກລັອກໄດ້. ກະລຸນາສ້າງໃບສັ່ງຂາຍໃໝ່ທີ່ເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ກັບໂຄງການນີ້."

#. module: sale_project_stock
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/sale_project_stock/models/stock_picking.py:0
msgid ""
"The Sales Order %(order)s linked to the Project %(project)s must be "
"validated before validating the stock picking."
msgstr ""
"ໃບສັ່ງຂາຍ %(order)s ທີ່ເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ກັບ ໂຄງການ %(project)s ຕ້ອງໄດ້ຮັບການຢືນຢັນກ່ອນທີ່ຈະຢືນຢັນການເບີກສ"
"າງ."

#. module: sale_project_stock
#: model_terms:ir.actions.act_window,help:sale_project_stock.stock_move_per_sale_order_line_action
msgid ""
"This menu gives you the full traceability of inventory\n"
"                operations on a specific product. You can filter on the product\n"
"                to see all the past or future movements for the product."
msgstr ""
"ເມນູນີ້ຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ທ່ານສາມາດຕິດຕາມການດຳເນີນງານສາງທັງໝົດຂອງສິນຄ້າໃດໜຶ່ງໄດ້. ທ່ານສາມາດກັ່ນຕອງຕາມສິນຄ້າເພື່"
"ອເບິ່ງການເຄື່ອນຍ້າຍທັງໝົດໃນອະດີດ ຫຼື ໃນອະນາຄົດຂອງສິນຄ້ານັ້ນໆ."

